div0.p:
On his coming to England this last Time, he contracted an Intimacy with one 


                  Joseph Machoi, (a Jew
               ) and together with him committed the Fact upon which he was convicted. He was not immediately concerned herein as an Agent, but only as a stander-by, to give Notice and Intimation of any Watchman, or other People, that might be supposed to prevent or discover their Designs, and was employed in receiving the Goods, or whatever else they stole, out of any House, and afterwards to sell them for his Companions.
